<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>24 Hour Radio Station — Project Proposal</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&family=DM+Mono:wght@300;400;500&family=Crimson+Pro:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;1,300&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
  <style>
    :root {
      --cream: #f5f0e8;
      --warm-white: #faf8f4;
      --brown: #3b2a1a;
      --rust: #b5451b;
      --gold: #c89a3c;
      --muted: #7a6a58;
      --border: #d6cbb8;
    }

    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    body {
      background-color: var(--cream);
      color: var(--brown);
      font-family: 'Crimson Pro', serif;
      font-size: 19px;
      line-height: 1.75;
    }

    /* ── HERO ── */
    .hero {
      background-color: var(--brown);
      color: var(--cream);
      padding: 80px 60px 60px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .hero::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: -60px; right: -60px;
      width: 360px; height: 360px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      border: 80px solid rgba(200,154,60,0.12);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .hero::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -40px; left: 40px;
      width: 220px; height: 220px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      border: 50px solid rgba(181,69,27,0.15);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .badge {
      display: inline-block;
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 11px;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gold);
      border: 1px solid var(--gold);
      padding: 4px 14px;
      border-radius: 2px;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: clamp(38px, 6vw, 72px);
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1.1;
      max-width: 700px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .hero h1 em {
      font-style: italic;
      color: var(--gold);
    }

    .hero-sub {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: rgba(245,240,232,0.75);
      max-width: 520px;
      font-style: italic;
    }

    /* ── LAYOUT ── */
    .container {
      max-width: 880px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 40px;
    }

    section {
      padding: 64px 0 40px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    section:last-of-type { border-bottom: none; }

    .section-label {
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 10px;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--rust);
      margin-bottom: 14px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
    }
    .section-label::after {
      content: '';
      flex: 1;
      height: 1px;
      background: var(--border);
    }

    h2 {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: clamp(24px, 3.5vw, 36px);
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 22px;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }

    h3 {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 400;
      font-style: italic;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: var(--brown);
    }

    p { margin-bottom: 16px; color: #4a3825; }
    p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

    /* ── QUOTE BLOCK ── */
    blockquote {
      border-left: 3px solid var(--gold);
      padding: 20px 28px;
      margin: 32px 0;
      background: var(--warm-white);
      font-style: italic;
      font-size: 20px;
      color: var(--brown);
    }

    /* ── PHASES ── */
    .phases { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 24px; margin-top: 10px; }

    .phase-card {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 56px 1fr;
      gap: 20px;
      align-items: start;
      background: var(--warm-white);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 24px 28px;
      border-radius: 2px;
      transition: border-color 0.2s;
    }
    .phase-card:hover { border-color: var(--gold); }

    .phase-num {
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 11px;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      color: var(--gold);
      font-weight: 500;
      padding-top: 4px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .phase-num span {
      display: block;
      font-size: 32px;
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      letter-spacing: 0;
      line-height: 1;
      margin-bottom: 2px;
    }

    /* ── OBSTACLES ── */
    .obstacles { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; margin-top: 10px; }

    @media (max-width: 600px) { .obstacles { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

    .obstacle {
      background: var(--warm-white);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 22px 24px;
      border-radius: 2px;
      border-top: 3px solid var(--rust);
    }

    .obstacle h4 {
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 11px;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--rust);
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    /* ── THEME ── */
    .theme-box {
      background: var(--brown);
      color: var(--cream);
      padding: 40px 44px;
      margin-top: 10px;
      border-radius: 2px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .theme-box::before {
      content: '"';
      position: absolute;
      top: -20px; right: 24px;
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 200px;
      color: rgba(200,154,60,0.08);
      line-height: 1;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .theme-box h3 {
      color: var(--gold);
      font-style: normal;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    .theme-box p {
      color: rgba(245,240,232,0.88);
      font-size: 20px;
      font-style: italic;
      max-width: 580px;
    }

    /* ── DELIVERABLES ── */
    .deliverables {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(220px, 1fr));
      gap: 16px;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    .deliverable {
      background: var(--warm-white);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 18px 20px;
      border-radius: 2px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .deliverable-icon {
      width: 32px;
      height: 32px;
      background: var(--cream);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .deliverable p {
      font-size: 16px;
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--brown);
    }

    /* ── FOOTER ── */
    footer {
      background: var(--brown);
      color: rgba(245,240,232,0.5);
      text-align: center;
      padding: 32px;
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 11px;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    }
    footer strong { color: var(--gold); }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <div class="hero">
    <div class="badge">Project Proposal</div>
    <h1>24 Hour <em>Radio</em><br/>Station</h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">A son fulfills his father's dream — one broadcast at a time.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="container">

    <!-- OVERVIEW -->
    <section>
      <div class="section-label">Overview</div>
      <h2>The Story Behind the Tower</h2>
      <p>
        Decades ago, husband and father Tom Donahue, dreamed of building a Catholic radio station — so much so that he bought a property with a 100-foot ham radio tower in the front yard. Life intervened. The tower stood silent.
      </p>
      <blockquote>
        "It ended up being their son, John, who went into Catholic media — in a certain sense, they still did build their Catholic radio station."
      </blockquote>
      <p>
        This project finally makes that dream real: a 24-hour temporary FM broadcast from that same tower, culminating in a father-and-son podcast filmed at sunset.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- PHASES -->
    <section>
      <div class="section-label">Structure</div>
      <h2>Project Phases</h2>
      <div class="phases">

        <div class="phase-card">
          <div class="phase-num"><span>01</span>PHASE</div>
          <div>
            <h3>Research & Legal Framework</h3>
            <p>Obtain a temporary FM broadcast license and determine the maximum legal transmission wattage for a short-term low-power event.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="phase-card">
          <div class="phase-num"><span>02</span>PHASE</div>
          <div>
            <h3>EWTN Partnership Outreach</h3>
            <p>Contact EWTN to get guidance on short-term FM broadcasting and request permission to air their Catholic programming during the 24-hour window.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="phase-card">
          <div class="phase-num"><span>03</span>PHASE</div>
          <div>
            <h3>Hardware Acquisition & Setup</h3>
            <p>Source and install FM transmission equipment on the existing 100-foot tower. Test signal and confirm everything is operational before go-live.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="phase-card">
          <div class="phase-num"><span>04</span>PHASE</div>
          <div>
            <h3>The 24-Hour Broadcast</h3>
            <p>Run the live FM broadcast and document the full experience on camera — including real-time obstacles and the moment the tower finally fulfills its purpose.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="phase-card">
          <div class="phase-num"><span>05</span>PHASE</div>
          <div>
            <h3>Sunset Podcast with Dad</h3>
            <p>At the close of the broadcast, sit down at sunset for a candid recorded conversation about the radio dream, fatherhood, and Catholic family life.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="phase-card">
          <div class="phase-num"><span>06</span>PHASE</div>
          <div>
            <h3>On-Camera Conclusion</h3>
            <p>A personal closing reflection on what the project revealed — especially the things learned for the first time in conversation with Dad.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- OBSTACLES -->
    <section>
      <div class="section-label">Challenges</div>
      <h2>Anticipated Obstacles</h2>
      <div class="obstacles">

        <div class="obstacle">
          <h4>Legal Licensing</h4>
          <p>Navigating FCC requirements for a temporary FM broadcast and determining the correct license and wattage limits.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="obstacle">
          <h4>24 Hours of Content</h4>
          <p>Filling a full broadcast requires a deep content library — hopefully solved through an EWTN programming agreement.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="obstacle">
          <h4>Hardware Setup</h4>
          <p>Sourcing FM transmitter equipment compatible with the existing tower and getting it tested and operational in time.</p>
        </div>



      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- THEME -->
    <section>
      <div class="section-label">Through Line</div>
      <h2>The Heart of the Project</h2>
      <div class="theme-box">
        <h3>Central Theme</h3>
        <p>
          Tom's primary vocation is husband and father — above any ambition or dream. This project is about magnanimity: the greatness of soul that ultimately enables sacrificial love and putting your family first. A tower silent for decades becomes, at last, proof of that truth.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- DELIVERABLES -->
    <section>
      <div class="section-label">Outputs</div>
      <div class="deliverables">
        <div class="deliverable">
          <div class="deliverable-icon">📻</div>
          <p>Completed 24-hour FM radio broadcast</p>
        </div>
        <div class="deliverable">
          <div class="deliverable-icon">🎙️</div>
          <p>Father-son podcast recording</p>
        </div>
        <div class="deliverable">
          <div class="deliverable-icon">🎬</div>
          <p>Long-form YouTube style episode</p>
        </div>
        <div class="deliverable">
          <div class="deliverable-icon">✝️</div>
          <p>EWTN partnership & content agreement</p>
        </div>
        <div class="deliverable">
          <div class="deliverable-icon">📋</div>
          <p>FCC temporary broadcast documentation</p>
        </div>
        <div class="deliverable">
          <div class="deliverable-icon">🏗️</div>
          <p>Operational FM transmitter on existing tower</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </div>

  <footer>
    <strong>24 Hour Radio Station</strong> &nbsp;·&nbsp; Project Proposal &nbsp;·&nbsp; Catholic Media
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
